<p><img src="/media/13092041/lapland-hotels-yllaskaltio-winter-time-1.jpg" alt="LaplandHotelHero" data-udi="umb://media/c69dcc96297c46b7a12cb1a1ad29446c" /></p>
<h2>Lapland Hotels</h2>
<p>Hotel stays are all about comfort, convenience and calmness. </p>
<p>You can enjoy comfy beds in your, room comfy sofas at the bar and comfy chairs in the restaurant - relax and put your feet up after a busy day of sight-seeing, <a data-udi="umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da" href="/{localLink:umb://document/bda83b0ac78e4ae8aa3f5206e06059da}" title="Lapland Excursions">excursions</a> or <a data-udi="umb://document/5c4dcb32caa44c5096ed1fc9494f0b29" href="/{localLink:umb://document/5c4dcb32caa44c5096ed1fc9494f0b29}" title="Skiing &amp; Snowboarding in Lapland, Finland">skiing</a>. </p>
<p>The convenience a hotel provides is some peoples idea of the perfect set-up. Breakfast buffets with all the choices to excellent and friendly staff available to offer turn-down service or provide directions. </p>
<p>Calmness is the perfect way to end the day or start a morning, with many hotels offering spa facilities where you can sit back and relax in the sauna, take a dip in the pool or quietly read a book on a lounger. </p>
<p>With <strong>10+ hotels</strong> to choose from across our Lapland resorts of <a data-udi="umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/1b2fbafe6b3546cbbcb8a26241bb809c}" title="Levi">Levi</a>, <a data-udi="umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c" href="/{localLink:umb://document/cc68d9ee210a4063af0a51552472263c}" title="Yllas">Yllas</a> and <a data-udi="umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5" href="/{localLink:umb://document/b8a6a8fa31c94e959dc5959c1881f2d5}" title="Saariselka">Saariselka</a> - we are sure there is a hotel for you. We've have selected just a few to get you started in your search. </p>
<p style="text-align: center;"><a data-udi="umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd" href="/{localLink:umb://document/25851216a21f4fddaee986c799f732cd}" title="Deals" class="c-btn">Lapland holiday deals</a></p>
</div>
<div>
<div class="col-xs-12 col-md-12">
<div></div>
</div>
